{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You live a simple life... until your Fate takes a sudden turn! You are a hero now. Sharpen your sword, win the hearts of your beautiful battle companions, and fulfill your Destiny, as it's you and only you who can protect your Homeland against all odds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/wl_eng.gif?t=1729658409\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your Destiny is Calling:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight through challenging battles and explore the deepest and darkest secrets of Enderion</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new units and upgrade your army to win this war!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friends with combat benefits?! Make new allies and bond with your hot companions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/front_girls2.jpg?t=1729658409\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 beautiful girls with unique personalities and battle roles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High-quality Live2D animations for all the girl's that will make your heart go doki-doki</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Professionally done full Japanese voice-over for all the girls</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than 20 intense battles with high replayability for you to explore</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An exciting story in a well-defined world for you to uncover!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Grand Marshal:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/char04.gif?t=1729658409\" />Despite being very young, this girl has become the commander-in-chief of the Ishan army. She is fierce, she is cunning, and she dominates any battlefield she sets her foot on. This is not a rose, but a real cactus! Are you be skilled enough to tame her? The reward may be very well worth it...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Empire\u2019s Commander:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/char01.gif?t=1729658409\" />Having worked her way up from a humble soldier, this girl is a formidable tactician on any battlefield. During one of the battles, she captured multiple enemy standards, and for this, the Emperor awarded her the rank of Commander. Will you win her devotion?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Barbarian Queen:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/char02.gif?t=1729658409\" />They say she is a brutish savage who is always willing to throw herself into the battle. At the same time, this wild beauty values honor and dignity above all else. Will she become your fierce nemesis or a passionate lover? Or could she be... both?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The High Sorceress:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/char03.gif?t=1729658409\" />Charming is a word that can exactly be used to describe her sweetness. She is pure as snow and her beauty is a thing to be admired. However, every rose has its thorns, so be sure not to fall to her charms too fast. Will you be the one to pick this flower?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Assassin:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/extras/storePage_char05.jpg?t=1729658409\" />She's a mystery that's waiting to be solved \u2013 and you have everything it takes to uncover her!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ready for Battle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/4f4a8355e6f4cbe32a639c031523ce4ad44fe1c9.jpg"},{"name":"Cannot Return Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/ee7972a0e62088b342d435473716df97ec445fad.jpg"},{"name":"It was Fun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/1da9feb7d40f986ab40623aa56d6df8d8189cd03.jpg"},{"name":"Misunderstanding","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/756e5606e99730cab30e9e94aa0829b10a52373b.jpg"},{"name":"Civil War","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/ddb8ed15ad84a18f56f810186feba2c286854cab.jpg"},{"name":"The Plot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/a54f7ae1aaa3df5fd0e437d91dc5fcf7d3c02a43.jpg"},{"name":"Passions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/9ea6437964b34c5de5f6f4c927e5e6231a37db37.jpg"},{"name":"Hero by Chance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/3675c7d677a1273bcbe87d21610f15bdc45dba81.jpg"},{"name":"Getting Stronger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/6d555026b52668976a4026b6e0a014b47810d370.jpg"},{"name":"Maximum Level","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1433420/e3faed3d370705597dd64cf09d91d35022527b63.jpg"}],"total":26},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1433420?t=1729658409","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1433420/page_bg_raw